<h1>Seller Policies</h1>

<h2>2.1 Listing Requirements</h2>

<ul>
  <li>**Accurate and detailed descriptions:** Provide accurate and detailed descriptions of all items, including condition, mileage, and any known defects.</li>
  <li>**High-quality photos:** Upload clear and high-quality photos of the item from multiple angles.</li>
  <li>**Clear pricing and shipping information:** Clearly state the price of the item and any applicable shipping costs.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2.2 Order Fulfillment</h2>

<ul>
  <li>**Timely and accurate order processing:** Process and ship orders promptly upon receipt of payment.</li>
  <li>**Provide tracking information:** Provide tracking information to buyers within 24hrs of shipment.</li>
  <li>**Address buyer inquiries:** Respond to buyer inquiries and concerns promptly and professionally.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2.3 Returns and Refunds</h2>

<ul>
  <li>**Return Policy:** Clearly state your return policy, including the timeframe for returns, eligibility criteria, and the return shipping process.</li>
  <li>**Refund Policy:** Clearly state your refund policy, including the timeframe for processing refunds and the method of refund (e.g., original payment method).</li>
</ul>

<h2>2.4 Product Authenticity</h2>

<p>**Ensure the authenticity of all parts sold.** You are responsible for verifying the authenticity of any parts you list on the Platform.</p>